                <head>281. Editorial Note.</head>
                <p>In preparation for spring 1969 session of the Eighteen-Nation Disarmament
                    Conference, a number of documents were generated by key government agencies
                    during February and March that deal with the issue of a comprehensive test ban
                    but appear in the chapter on the “Eighteen-Nation Disarmament Committee, Spring
                    Session,1969.”</p>
            </div>
